data.description: Price improvement on this exceptional home in an exceptional community.  Pool and tennis courts are within walking distance.  This large home home once a model home has a finished garage that could be an office or an additional family room - lots of possibilities.  Many features include new carpet on the stairs and second floor.  New flooring in the family room highlights the 2-story stone fireplace located off the kitchen, also a new washer and dryer in the first floor laundry room.  Lots of windows make it bright and airy.  Sitting area / sun room in the kitchen as well as countertop sitting for large groups.  The master bedroom is spacious enhanced with a cathedral ceiling, an ensuite with soaking tub and shower and double vanities.  This home is being sold fully furnished and is move-in ready.  Make an appointment to see this one!!!
